  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK710">
<l>nuṇṇiya meṉpā raḷakkuṅkōl kāṇuṅkāṟ</l>
<l>kaṇṇalla tillai piṟa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The measuring-rod of those (ministers) who say "we are acute" will on inquiry be found to be their (own) eyes and nothing else.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
